Friday, October 11, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

95-1924. Hill v. Urbana.

Champaign App. No. 94-CA-22. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Champaign County. Upon consideration of the motion of R.E. Holland Excavating, Inc., to participate in oral argument,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to participate in oral argument be, and hereby is, granted.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that no additional time will be allotted.
